      "writtenOn": "2018-06-11T23:38:01Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i am not sure this much improves the situation. If someone added a repo, it won\u0027t be in blamelistLogs. Worst case, someone will receive an email during the time of transition, which is not a big deal.\nI think we can either retry the whole thing if whitelist changed, just let it go and not do this check altogether",
